==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: hàixǐ 

===Noun===
'''[[害]][[喜]]'''

# [[morning sickness]]
#: ''[[無論]][[是]][[曾經]][[懷孕]][[或]][[準備]][[懷孕]][[的]][[女性]]，[[一]][[聽]][[到]]“'''害喜'''”，[[大多]][[會]][[產生]][[些許]][[恐懼]]、[[抗拒]][[的]][[心理]]。'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])
#: ''[[无论]][[是]][[曾经]][[怀孕]][[或]][[准备]][[怀孕]][[的]][[女性]]，[[一]][[听]][[到]]“'''害喜'''”，[[大多]][[会]][[产生]][[些许]][[恐惧]]、[[抗拒]][[的]][[心理]]。'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])
#: ''Hearing the term "'''morning sickness'''" will spark a certain amount of fear and apprehension in most women, regardless of whether they have been pregnant or are planning on being pregnant.''

